caption: I admire this place! They have good meals, their menu is rich, The chef in that restaurant is a professional, I enjoy a lot tasting all their food. The dishes are always good, the service towards the customers  is friendly. I visit often this place and I was never discontended. I recommend it to all my friends.

Ordered this on grubhub and all I can say is bad. Your pricy bbq box comes with 3 slices of brisket /wings /and Mac.  Atleast for the price let the food be good.  The brisket was just dry, tasteless and bad. The Mac and cheese was worst. Some of the noodles weren't even fully cooked. The wings were decent.  The delivery came on time but being the first time eating as this establishment I can't recommend the food at all. I'm sorry to say.
Had a fantastic experience in this spot with my wife. The food came quickly and the customer service is just awesome. Prices are affordable.

From the moment  you enter that place  they give you an agreeable feeling. Very friendly stuff, it is a kind restaurant to  enjoy with your friends or with your date. delicious  cuisine, experienced  chef de cuisine, modest  cost and courteous  service. Warmly recommended.
I honestly liked their dishes and customer service, awesome area nearby to my apartment. The employees are always welcoming. Would recommend to others.
Awesome food, helpful staff, consistently excellent vibes. They charge fair pricing and the food quality is very good. 5 stars.

This restaurant is definitely one of the finest place in the neighborhood. Anytime I come to this place I am exceedingly satisfied. They maintain their very high  standard service and the topmost level of dishes  they offer. You no doubt will love this restaurant. Warmly  recommended.
Great food, very friendly staff members, constantly fantastic vibes. They charge convenient prices and the food quality is awesome. 5 stars.
bbq, very tasty. i wanted to post a food pic but it looked so good i couldn't stop. the staff was very friendly and attentive. menu is like a cafe in indianapolis i loved.
The service is constantly efficient, excellent atmosphere, very welcoming staff. I will visit again when I am nearby.

I meet friends in this lovely spot often! This is my favorite spot to grab a bite.  I visit this place routinely. The food is very good, the staff members are courteous and the prices are reasonable. I enjoy meeting in this spot over a tasty dinner.

I celebrated my graduation today in this gorgeous place. Well we passed a great evening and the venue was undoubtedly the reason for that outstanding evening. The stuff  participated in a gorgeous manner, the food was yummy and my guests were very  delighted. We shall surely visit again for more events. thanks very much.
Had a awesome experience in this spot with my kids. The food came rapidly and the service is just great. Prices are affordable.
Great and flavorful food, I like the mood this place has, and the cashiers were kind. I will surely come back in the future.

Last week was our first time we came to that excellent restaurant. But It is no doubt not the last time. We had a good time with the generous service, with the superb  cuisine and booze and with the decent price. We will no doubt come back in a short time.
I had the brisket sandwich out of this world,you can tell the meat was smoked for a very long time because you could taste all the Smokey flavor in the meat it’s a must try
Great food, great service will come back again I recommend this place to eat, is delish!!!
Had a awesome experience here with my kid. The food came quickly and the customer service is just awesome. Prices are fair.

I celebrated my nomination yesterday in this excellent restaurant. happy to tell that we passed a awesome evening and the restaurant was unquestionably one of the reasons for that successful meeting. The waiters  participated in a sweet way, the cuisine was extremely good and my buddies were so  delighted. We shall no dout return for more joyful events. Thank you very much.

I like to go with friends to this restaurant with my highest recommendations. I  go to this restaurant often. I get very good feedback from my friends. The the cooking is delicious and the crew is welcoming and cooperative. Every time  we visit this place we have a pleasant time.  warmly recommended.
The brisket waffle fries were huge! YUM!!
The fries and bbq are delicious and to die for. They do NOT skip on the meat and everything always tastes fresh and amazing. This place is a real treat. 😋
I simply like their dishes. I always get fantastic service here. The place is neat and the staff members are always very nice. I highly recommend this place.

Fletcher’s bbq. Besides for the brisket being dry,  the culture at your establishment screams WE DO NOT CARE ABOUT THE CUSTOMER! Shame, as you’re paying a fortune in fees, rent & payroll. Might as well give the customer a decent experience. Your employees are unenthusiastic (costing you money) and no one wants to order from a kiosk people actually have questions about your food. You’re not McDonalds...
This place is worth trying. They serve large portions for convenient prices. Regularly well organized and with awesome atmosphere. Will come visit again.

I used to be a big fan of this place, but the customer service is so bad. Very unfriendly. I live a block away and this was my go to place in the Dekalb market hall, but since they put in those self pay kiosks the employees seemed burdened with less staff during a Friday lunch service. The food quality has gone down as well.... it too bad I used to frequent this place one a week and I’m done with it. I’ll spend my money elsewhere. Maybe the owner should show up and work a shift to see the dysfunction.
I had an amazing time at this spot. We liked the great environment and the meals. The staff members were super amiable. I am glad we eventually managed to visit here.
The service is regularly speedy, good ambience, helpful staff. I will eat here again when I get here.
I simply enjoy their food. I always get good service there. The place is well organised and the staff members are always very friendly. Will come visit again.

I must say I was definitely disappointed by the wings I had recently. I had your wings before, roughly 6 months to one year ago, and they were phenomenal. However, on this recent visit, they were awful...The wings were fried to the point it looked burnt and were absolutely tasteless...Did you all forget to season them before frying them and don’t you tell your workers to monitor the product while it’s cooking? What happened to the juicy, flavorful wings I had in the past? Won’t be back until you all fix what is wrong...

I’m from Tn and smoke my own meats. I did not eat here however, old school rule is. You eat with your eyes first. This place looked amazing, Will eating pizza at the next door neighbors which was lousy! I watched them build a pulled pork sand. Huge pile is meat on the bun and sauces up. Definitely gonna give this a try next time I’m in Brooklyn... my 5 stars are on appearance only but I can tell that meat is good.
The place serves large dishes and for fair pricing. very kind employees. Will visit again.

Really great ribs. Very tender and actual meat on the bone. I like the sauce, which comes on the side. I tried the wings first and they were ok, they're pretty good but the ribs are great. I read the reviews and thought why even try but they were old reviews.  Rico was the person who waited on me and he was friendly, nice and nothing like the other reviews. Yeah you know everything in the Dekalb Market is pricey but so what, just give them a try.
Fast, warm, delicious
If I could rate a zero I would. HORRIBLE @
I had the bbq chicken sandwhich. The chicken was lacked any kind of "smokey" flavor. It was really cold and dry. Just a smattering of bbq sauce with lots of bits dry chicken. HORRIBLE.
Great Wings

(Translated by Google) I had never eaten such an expensive and bad sandwich, the potatoes and the salad are not left behind, the staff is not friendly, rather I would say indifferent and rude with the needs of the client, they are slow to serve, rather bad the place.  (Original) Nunca había comido un sanwich tan caro y tan malo , las papas y la ensalada no se quedan atrás,  el personal no es amable , más bien diría indiferente y rudo con las necesidades del cliente , se tardan en servir,  bastante malo el lugar .
Clean food. No grease or grime.

Sooooo for $14 you get scraps of dry pork with a lil BBQ sauce, that the store bought potato roll soaks up entirely.  That on top on the fact that the lil West Indian boy (actually quite tall) has an attitude that screams he'd rather not work.  Never coming back & telling all my friends/co-workers, ixnay on LetchersFay.  Oh and the guy making sandwiches keeps touching his phone.  What in the CDC is going on here
Great sandwich overall for price.  Needs more sauce though.

The driest meat I have ever tasted. It wasn’t fresh because when I first bit into it, it was cold. The fries weren’t evenly seasoned so one tasted better, bland or salty. The cornbread is not worth your time, I ate it and just thought about how I wasted $10 but I need to eat because I have to work. I was shocked because it was lunchtime, which is known for being the best time to order from restaurants. Sigh.

Had the Chicken Sandwich Weekday Lunch special.  Cube chicken with BBQ sauce in a potato bun, waffle fries, and cole slaw.  The chicken was alright, the frozen fries were fries to a nice crisp, and the cole slaw was alright, but for its price, it's a pretty reasonable deal at city point.
Laziest workers.... Literally stood around for 10 mins then started making the order. I was the only customer....
Filthy with a side of attitude served cold. Be prepared to wait as the cashier flirts, and she plays with his hair. Hold the herpes, please.

Had a pulled pork sandwich. Meat & BBQ sauce we’re almost two separate things. i.e. Sauce was added like ketchup on a burger. Bun was a Martin’s potato hamburger bun, which was totally inadequate for this sandwich. Ate half with a fork. Pork was tasty, but would have been much better with the sauce mixed in. Disappointed overall.

I thought it be a fun gesture to try this barbecue out & being from the south, I don't take this lightly... They gave me plenty of meat but there was no flavor at all! Theres an employee there (I don't know her name but for identification purposes, an Asian girl) who gave a small squirt of BBQ on top... But it was so dry I asked her to grab a side a barbecue sauce.... she said she would get it for me but I never got it as she ended up ignoring me. I really didn't like this girl's attitude.. not friendly at all! I will not go back.
Sauce is decent, but meat is dried out and lacking flavor.

This was actually really good. I did the lunch deal and the chicken sandwich was a thigh and had great smoke flavor. The buffalo wings were really good. Smoke flavor and buffalo sauce with a great crisp from the frier. The waffle fries were done to order. Ribs looked great, I didn't have them but I will next time. With the lunch deal it was a great price. Highly recommend.
More people should know about this place. The prices are solid and the food is legit.
Delicious food. Succulent and tender. Best BBQ sauce in Brooklyn. Prices kinda high, but as is everything in the market hall.
